---
description: Senior Rust engineer Git/GitHub — commit/pull often
alwaysApply: true
---
- Commit often: small atomic commits. One logical change per commit.
- Pull before push: git pull --rebase before git push.
- Commit messages: imperative, <72 chars.
- Branch: feature branches for non-trivial work; main deployable.
- Pre-push: cargo check / cargo test before push.
